<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
   <head>
      <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
   </head>
   <body>
      <h1>Your Movie was favorited by <%= @favoritemovie.user.vname %></h1>
      <p>Congratulations <%= @favoritemovie.movie.user.vname %> your
         movie <%= @favoritemovie.movie.title %> was favorited by another
         user. You must feel pretty proud to receive this recognition.
         All the time you spent on creating your movie must have really
         paid off. As a celebration of your efforts we would like to
         give you a special prize.
      </p>
      <p>As a reward for your efforts we have decide to give you
         <%= @points %> points. We hope you can find something to
         use it on our little petsite. I hope this will encourage
         you to create even more content and raise your motivation.
      </p>
      <br>
      <p>From the Duelingpets Staff</p>
   </body>
</html>
